data.meta_description: Information about our projects. Takasago Thermal Engineering provides comprehensive system engineering services with a focus on air conditioning. We use advanced technologies that will last for years to come, and offer a wide range of services from planning and design to construction and maintenance in all types of buildings, factories and facilities.
data.text: FeaturesThis facility leads marketing and new business creations, for automotive, IoT, energy, healthcare fields. Based on the concept of "a place to inspire future engineers," the public facility, "Mulabo!" is also opened to convey children the fun of science through electronics.
